title: Talaash: The Hunt Begins
subTitle: Arjun grows up to be a high-profile vigilante after his father's murder and sister's abduction. Soon, he vows revenge and sets out on a mission to find his sister.

title: Ram Aur Shyam
subTitle: Ram escapes from his home when he learns that his abusive brother-in-law plans to kill him. Justice is meted out when Shyam, Ram's long-lost twin, accidentally takes his place.

title: Naagin Bani Suhaagan
subTitle: Vaishali, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, is blessed with a boon to transform herself into a shapeshifting snake. She falls into a dilemma when circumstances force her to go against her love.

title: Dharam Kanta
subTitle: A dacoit's plan goes wrong when a kidnapped child is killed after the ransom is exchanged. The boy's devastated mother curses the dacoit, who then starts to suffer the consequences of his crime.

title: Main Hoon Na
subTitle: Major Ram is given orders to go undercover as a college student to protect a general's daughter from a rogue soldier. He must also fulfil his dying father's desire to reconcile with his family.

title: Ghar Ghar Ki Kahani
subTitle: Ram begins to suspect that his wife, Seeta, is having an affair with his brother, Amar. His suspicion remains even after Amar gets married, creating problems within his family.

title: Gharwali Baharwali
subTitle: Arun inadvertently ties the knot with Manisha and even has a child with her. He keeps this a secret from his first wife Kaajal. It is only a matter of time before his life starts to unravel.

title: Jeet
subTitle: Karan, a gangster, falls in love with Kajal, but she marries Raju because of her father's poor health. Later, when Raju finds out about his father's illegal business, Karan is hired to kill him.

title: Izzatdaar
subTitle: When Brahm Dutt, a wealthy businessman, is falsely convicted on murder charges, he enlists the help of a boy to exact revenge on Indrajeet, his cruel son-in-law and the cause of all his miseries.

title: Izzatdaar
subTitle: When Brahm Dutt, a wealthy businessman, is falsely convicted on murder charges, he enlists the help of a boy to exact revenge on Indrajeet, his cruel son-in-law and the cause of all his miseries.

title: Aakhri Adalat
subTitle: An honest police officer decides to take the law into his own hands when he loses his job, and the thugs he caught get released due to some technicality.

title: Zulm Ka Badla
subTitle: Verma adopts Geeta, the orphaned daughter of his friend, who grows up to marry his son, Anil. However, when a gangster dies during Anil's probe, both men suspect that Geeta is responsible.

title: Salaakhen
subTitle: An honest schoolteacher commits suicide due to the actions of the family of a man he testified against. In retaliation, his son takes the law into his own hands and seeks revenge.

title: Ready
subTitle: A case of mistaken identities causes Prem and Sanjana to fall in love. Meanwhile, Sanjana's uncles try to get the money that she has inherited and Prem convinces them to marry her off to him.

title: Elaan
subTitle: A.C.P. Ramakant Chaudhary, an uptight police officer, struggles with bringing his elder son's killers to justice. Vishal, his younger son, decides to take matters in his own hands.

title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Krodh
subTitle: Karan struggles to raise his five younger sisters and wants them to lead good lives. However, he is heartbroken when his sister, Asha, marries against his wishes and later, her marriage fails.

title: Yodha
subTitle: Karan, a lawyer, and Suraj, a victim of fate, find themselves fighting for the same cause when they take on the anti-social elements to rid the society of its ills.

title: Yodha
subTitle: Karan, a lawyer, and Suraj, a victim of fate, find themselves fighting for the same cause when they take on the anti-social elements to rid the society of its ills.

title: Ekka Raja Rani
subTitle: Talented dancer, Barkha, saves the life of an underground crime boss, VK, who offers her a job as repayment. Later VK falls for Barkha, but she is in love with another man.

title: Vaada Raha...I Promise
subTitle: Duke Chawla leads a perfect life with a good job and a beautiful girlfriend. However, when he meets with an accident, his life changes forever.

title: Bhabhi
subTitle: After finding out the true reason of her husband marrying her, a woman is rescued by her brother-in-law. Both of them subsequently decide to teach her in-laws a lesson.

title: Banjaran
subTitle: The universe offers a Banjara tribe leader's daughter an opportunity to turn her doomed love story into a happily-ever-after with her soulmate.

title: Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge
subTitle: While travelling across Europe, Raj and Simran unexpectedly grow close, only to be separated by family expectations, prompting Raj to fight for love and tradition.

title: Sainik
subTitle: When Lieutenant Suraj goes missing, his father believes he is dead and decides to keep the news from his daughter and his son's wife. However, they already know and choose to put up a brave front.

title: Movie
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Vishwanath
subTitle: Vishwanath, an honest lawyer, is framed and imprisoned due to a gangster. After his release, he sets out to seek revenge and ends up becoming a criminal.
